definitions.definition: A hole or hollow depression in a solid object.

subdefinitions.definition: A hollow area within the body .
The female part of a mold : the depression itself or ( metonymically ) the half of the mold that contains it.

definitions.definition: A small or large hole in a tooth caused by caries ; often also a soft area adjacent to the hole also affected by caries.
examples: Jim got two cavities filled at the dentist's office yesterday.

main_definition: A hole or hollow depression in a solid object.
